[color=#ffff00]Click and drag[/color] the tiles to reveal squares from the hidden art underneath.

Some tiles have [color=#ffff00]numbered requirements[/color]. These tiles can only be inside a revealed area of size that matches their required number of squares. For example, a requirement of [color=#ffff00]4[/color] must be within a revealed area of one of these dimensions, [color=#ffff00]no matter the location[/color]:







You can start revealing from [color=#ffff00]any tile[/color], not just the numbered ones. You also have up to 5 chances to [color=#ffff00]undo[/color] your last move. Finally, complete the artwork to advance, or click the reset button to retry.
